# 44 - Simple Convergence Example
# Basic CONVERGE without multi-agent - self-refining summarization

NAME converge-simple

INPUT content
INPUT max_words DEFAULT "100"

CONVERGE summarize """Summarize the following content in $max_words words or less:

$content

Review your summary and refine it for:
- Clarity and conciseness  
- Coverage of key points
- Readability

Continue refining until further changes would not meaningfully improve the summary.""" -> summary WITHIN 5

RUN main USING summarize
